data.title: Watch Violet Evergarden (2018) TV Series Online
data.meta_description: Where to watch Violet Evergarden (2018) starring Yui Ishikawa, Daisuke Namikawa, Takehito Koyasu and directed by Shinpei Sawa.
data.text: In the aftermath of a great war, Violet Evergarden, a young female ex-soldier, gets a job at a writers' agency and goes on assignments to create letters that can connect people.
